#: 2021-03-04-regenerative-agriculture-feed-world.md:171
msgid ""
"![A male rice farmer carries harvested rice as he walks alongside a sunny "
"rice paddy](/assets/uploads/876534c6-020f-442c-bb93-833a8f5e5965.jpg)"
msgstr ""
"![Ein Reisbauer trägt seine Ernte an einem sonnigen Reisfeld vorbei](/assets/"
"uploads/876534c6-020f-442c-bb93-833a8f5e5965.jpg)"

